description:
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly motivated and experienced Clinical Secretary to work in the Women&#39;s Health Department working directly to the clinical team at the Conquest Hospital. Clinical secretaries are responsible for the provision of a proactive, responsive and professional secretarial service to the Clinical team. Highly self motivated, you will possess the ability to work with minimal supervision and to deliver high quality work to tight deadlines. You will have proven experience of managing competing priorities and planning and prioritising your work effectively. You will thrive on working in a busy unit and as part of a team. A flexible and proactive approach is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to deal with patients, clinicians and other staff members, ensuring high levels of customer service. You will have regular interaction with the clinical secretarial management team and the departmental service manager. It is essential that you are able to demonstrate good interpersonal, verbal and written skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have a proven track record of recent secretarial and office experience in a fast paced environment with a good level of IT literacy and Microsoft Office skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This dynamic role will keep you both challenged and busy as you work closely with colleagues to support the clinical team of consultants, junior doctors and specialist nurses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience of working in a NHS hospital environment and knowledge of medical terminology is advantageous.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a challenging yet rewarding position. Potential applicants should ensure they meet the minimum criteria on the person specification before applying for this role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time post of 37.5 hours per week to be worked Monday-Friday in core office hours&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note: This advert may close early if a high volume of applications are received&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shani Adams&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clinical Secretarial Team Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shani.adams@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
